# EduCore Web — Environment Variables
# Copy to apps/web/.env and adjust for your deployment.

# --- Development (localhost) ---
# Leave VITE_API_URL commented out. Vite's dev server proxies
# /api/* → http://localhost:4000 automatically.
#
# --- Production ---
# Set VITE_API_URL to your deployed API base URL:
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com/api/v1
#
# The value is baked into the build at `vite build` time.
